compare-index-looking-for-a-better-browser = ¿Buscas un navegador mejor? Compararemos { -brand-name-firefox } con { -brand-name-chrome }, { -brand-name-edge }, { -brand-name-safari }, { -brand-name-opera }, { -brand-name-brave } e { -brand-name-ie } para ayudarte a tomar una decisión.
